孤岛中的快递员：有人在汉口站网点转给他500元感谢费，他没有收。
Dispatch in the island: someone in Hankou station network transfer to him 500 yuan thank-you fee, he did not receive.
李紫宸2020-02-10 21:20。
Li Zichen 2020-02-10 21: 20.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网记者李紫宸疫情让武汉成为矗立在中国中部的一个孤岛，快递成为这座孤岛与外界建立物质联系的重要通道之一。
The outbreak of Li Zichen, a reporter from the Economic Watch Network, made Wuhan an isolated island in central China, making express delivery one of the important ways to establish material contact with the outside world.
1月23日封城之后，快递的工作变得不同寻常。
After the closure of the city on January 23, express delivery became unusual.
。
.
岳辉，湖北武汉人，湖北顺丰武汉常青分部王家墩营业点的一名普通收派员。
Yuehui, Hubei Wuhan, Hubei Shunfeng Wuhan Changqing branch Wang Jiadun business point of a general dispatcher.
今年是他在顺丰的第三个年头。
This year is his third year in Shunfeng.
。
.
汉口火车站及周边2公里区域是岳辉日常的派送区域。
Hankou railway station and the surrounding 2 km area is Yue Hui's daily sending area.
疫情之前，这里是武汉最喧嚣热闹的区域之一，但此时这里像按下了停止键，安静、冷清。
Before the outbreak, this is Wuhan is one of the most noisy and noisy areas, but here like to press the stop button, quiet, cold.
。
.
疫情期间，岳辉的工作没有停歇过。
During the epidemic, Yue's work did not stop.
顺丰是一家365天营业的企业，在武汉这个疫情最严峻的城市，保证医疗保障物资和市民的生活物资正常收派的任务就更为艰巨。
Shunfeng is a 365-day business enterprise, in Wuhan, the most serious epidemic in the city, to ensure medical supplies and normal distribution of life and materials to the task of more difficult.
。
.
岳辉的出门防护装备包括口罩、护目镜，防护服、医用手套、消毒液，他会对即将派送的快件进行消毒。
Yuehui's protective gear including masks, goggles, protective clothing, medical gloves, disinfectant, he will disinfect the soon-to-be-delivered express.
防护和消毒工作之后，他将骑车前往汉口火车站的财神广场，开始一天的派送。
After protection and disinfection, he will cycle to Hankou Railway Station MaiShen Square to start the day's delivery.
。
.
岳辉告诉记者，因疫情的影响，再加上旁边就是华南海鲜市场，他所在片区的很多小区都实行了封闭管理，外来人员一律不得进入。
Yuehui told reporters that due to the impact of the epidemic, and the side of the South China seafood market, he is located in a number of small areas are closed management, no one is allowed to enter.
。
.
“往常的八九点是正常派件时间，但放在被疫情打乱的生活节奏中，就显得有些早，所以经常在接通电话后，电话那边传来的是责备和不满。
"Normally, eight or nine o'clock is normal dispatch time, but it's a little early to be in the midst of a life disrupted by an epidemic, so often when you get a call, there's blame and dissatisfaction.
”2月5日，岳辉向记者无奈表示，“在跟客户电话联系之后，岳辉就在小区门口等着在家的客户出来取件。
"On February 5, Yue Hui told reporters helplessly," Yue Hui waited at the door of the community to pick up pieces after calling customers.
有时候客户很快就会出来，但也有被一些事情耽误不能马上出来拿件的，所以派送的时间和难度会大很多。
Sometimes the customer will come out quickly, but there are some things delay can not get out immediately, so the delivery time and difficulty will be much larger.
”。
"
在疫区，特别是每天往返在如此靠近传染源头的危险区域，即便是普通人都会谨慎到绕道而行。
In affected areas, especially in dangerous areas so close to the source of infection, even ordinary people are careful to make devious detours.
没有担忧是不可能的，岳辉坦言，在疫情曝光初期，自己在华南海鲜市场收派件，也很害怕，但是职责所在，不能说有风险的地方就不送。
It is impossible to worry, admitted Yue, in the early days of the outbreak, his delivery in the South China seafood market, but also very scared, but the duty, can not say that there are risks where not to send.
“做好防护，心态放好，相信医学，相信国家，相信自己是可以去执行任务的。
"Protect yourself, put your mind to good use, believe in medicine, trust the country and believe that you can do your job.
”岳辉说。
"said Yueh-hui.
。
.
根据顺丰提供的数据，从1月24日到2月9日，顺丰航空累计执行航班58个，运输防疫物资1183吨。
From January 24 to February 9, Shunfeng carried out a cumulative total of 58 flights, transporting 1183 tons of epidemic prevention materials, according to data provided by Shunfeng.
顺丰全网合计运输4065万件包裹至湖北。
Shunfeng total network transport 40.65 million parcels to Hubei.
。
.
疫情期间，岳辉所属的顺丰依然为一线人员调拨了大量的生活物资，有饺子、面、饼干、水果、饮用水等，用以保障网点员工的日常生活。
During the epidemic, Yue Hui's Shunfeng still allocates a large amount of living materials to the front-line staff, including dumplings, noodles, biscuits, fruit, drinking water, etc., to ensure the daily life of network employees.
在个人安全保障方面，下发了口罩、护目镜、消毒液、、医用手套、防护服等，并每日提醒员工佩戴和消毒。
In the area of personal safety and security, masks, goggles, disinfectant, medical gloves, protective clothing, etc., were issued and staff were reminded to wear and disinfect them daily.
为了减少人员接触，确保收寄安全，公司在武汉提供自寄自取为主的收派件服务。
In order to reduce personal contact and ensure the security of mail, the company in Wuhan to provide self-sent mail-based delivery services.
。
.
岳辉回忆，2月1日，财神广场有个客户来到网点取件，根据客户提供的单号，网点再三查找未找到该件，由于这是一批送到医院的医疗物资，当天是承诺的最后交货期限，如果不能及时找到并派送，一方面会影响医院的正常使用，另一方面也会对寄件人的业务和信誉造成影响。
Yue Hui recalled that on February 1, a customer in Maishen Square came to pick up the item. According to the list provided by the customer, the site repeatedly searched for it. As it was a shipment of medical supplies to the hospital, the promised delivery date would affect the normal use of the hospital and the sender's business and reputation.
。
.
对方的焦灼被岳辉看在眼里，他迅速联系客户联动多部门协同查找，快件最终在吴家山中转场找到了。
The other party's anxiety was seen by Yue Hui, he quickly linked with the multi-departmental search, the express in Wujiashan finally found.
。
.
在中转场，寄件人拿到快件后很感动，当即通过微信给岳辉转了500元作为感谢，不过，这笔感谢费，岳辉只是心领了，并没有接收。
In the middle of the transfer, the sender was very moved to get the express, and immediately passed a micro-letter to Yuehui 500 yuan as a thank-you, but this thank-you fee, Yue Hui just received, did not receive.
。
.
2月3日傍晚，一封特殊的求助函辗转送到了王家墩网点。
On the evening of February 3, a special letter of help was sent to the Wang Pier branch.
该求助函请求顺丰协助将一批医疗护目镜转寄到鄂州。
The letter asked Shunfeng to help forward a batch of medical goggles to Huizhou.
这批物资是一家社会慈善社团募资购买的，原本由浙江发往鄂州，但电商在发货操作时误发到了武汉，此时，重新购买面临着有钱无货的情况，更为无奈的是，此时湖北省由于交通管制，已经暂停了省内城市间的寄递。
The goods were collected by a social charity and sent from Zhejiang to Huizhou, but the electric merchants sent the goods to Wuhan by mistake during the delivery operation. At this time, the purchase was faced with the situation of having no money, and even more so, because of traffic control, Hubei Province has suspended inter-city delivery.
。
.
了解到事情缘由后，岳辉决定向公司反映。
After learning the reason of the matter, Yue Hui decided to report to the company.
在当时，尽管一般的物件无法发运，但单独的医药物资运输，有通行证的情况下，还能协调。
At that time, although general items could not be shipped, individual shipments of medical supplies could be coordinated where permits were available.
他的反馈得到了落实。
His feedback was followed up.
在经多方核实后，该批物资在2月5日最终抵达了鄂州防控指挥小组。
After being verified by many parties, the shipment finally arrived at the Huizhou control and command group on February 5.
。
.
采访中岳辉说：“这个时候，我会觉得自己面对的不仅仅是一份工作，而是一份责任。
"At this point, I feel like I'm dealing not just with a job, but with a responsibility," Zhongyuehui said.
我护送的是一件件物资，一个个护目镜，但是我知道，我是在为守护更多人的生活。
I was escorting supplies and goggles, but I knew I was taking care of more people.
”。
"
